result.name: Taste Full Kitchen

reviews.text: A local dim sum restaurant offering surprisingly tasty food and service at reasonable price.  Table was easily available in the late morning.
Good
Nice seafood, not expensive.
真味鮮廚座落於旺角閙市中，地點適宜朋友間、同事、晚間飯局聚會。但出品只是尚算可以，在本人歷次飯局中有許多次不愉快經歷，有二次上湯焗龍蝦，店家用死去龍蝦給與客戶食用，燒鵝亦試過用放了一段長時間出品給與客食用，（即是不新鮮）有一次點咗一盆刺身發現有一隻活生生蟑螂在裝飾盆景內走動，廚房出品食物不能保持水準，時好時壞。

除門口比較有禮外
入到去由帶錯桌，掉下一張點心卡就走
杯筷，茶水，點心紙都要叫人先拎，叫侍應？。。。當然唔係易事

點完點心後，無啦啦一個阿姐指👉住大大聲話「寫錯枱呀你地」

咁好服務，問點解baby都要計茶位？ 佢大大聲話，你張6人枱，你地唔係想4 個人坐咁大張枱下嘛？ 

今時今日咁既服務，無下次

reviews.text: Is quite normal. I am quite disappointed about the floor. It is very wet and slippery and a bit expensive. This restaurant is not the best choices in Hong Kong.

Best ever.  Best Roast Goose you'll ever find in Hong Kong and Kowloon they have many restaurants all over the city. Best of all is their prices are extremely reasonable sometimes unbelievably cheap and the food quality is always consistent ( for the past 10 years).  Must eat restaurant for locals and travelers!!!!!!!
Food was good ! But the hygiene is not really up to standard. Hope they can improve that
Must pre-order the king crab as you r most likely not able to order it if you didnt reserve.
The food is nice, but there are a lot of seats in a small space..
